<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OKR 提交提醒</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 640px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 24px;
            background: #f3f4f6;
        }
        .email-container {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        }
        .header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dc2626;
            padding-bottom: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #dc2626;
            margin: 8px 0 0;
        }
        .panel {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .label {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: 96px;
        }
        .value {
            color: #111827;
        }
        .warning {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
            padding: 16px 18px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 28px 0 20px;
        }
        .cta a {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #111827;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 28px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">OKR 绩效考核系统</div>
            <div class="title">提交提醒</div>
        </div>

        <p>{{recipientName}}，您好：</p>
        <p>以下 OKR 考核事项目前仍待您处理，请尽快完成提交：</p>

        <div class="panel">
            <div><span class="label">考核名称</span><span class="value">{{assessmentTitle}}</span></div>
            <div><span class="label">考核周期</span><span class="value">{{period}}</span></div>
            {{#if endDate}}
            <div><span class="label">截止时间</span><span class="value">{{endDate}}</span></div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        <div class="warning">
            <strong>待处理事项：</strong>
            <ul>
                {{#each pendingItems}}
                <li>{{participantName}}（{{waitingFor}}）</li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="cta">
            <a href="{{systemUrl}}">进入 OKR 系统处理</a>
        </div>

        <p>如已完成，请忽略本邮件；如存在异常，请联系系统管理员。</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>此邮件由 OKR 绩效考核系统自动发送，请勿直接回复。</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
